{"tid":1175892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：港航飛成田客機3天6零件脫落　日本當局稱不尋常","createTime":"2019-05-29T00:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T01:37:42.000Z","uid":5523,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae8056848f3793877498978480d742848e567e7","tid":1175892,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T00:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190529/s00001/08d29b94d0589d41db2949a81f76b6fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190529%2Fs00001%2F08d29b94d0589d41db2949a81f76b6fd.jpg&h=3eca3c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本放送協會報道，周日（26日）至周二（28日）期間，香港航空飛往日本成田機場的多班客機中，出現燈罩、螺絲等6件零件脫落。<br />\n<br />\n成田機場一度關閉跑道檢查，導致航班延誤，惟未有在跑道發現脫落零件，相信零件是飛行中途脫落。<br />\n<br />\n國土交通省認為事件不尋常，香港航空正調查原因。<br />\n<br />\n（日本放送協會）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190529/s00001/1559087939995/%e6%97%a5%e5%aa%92-%e6%b8%af%e8%88%aa%e9%a3%9b%e6%88%90%e7%94%b0%e5%ae%a2%e6%a9%9f3%e5%a4%a96%e9%9b%b6%e4%bb%b6%e8%84%ab%e8%90%bd-%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e7%95%b6%e5%b1%80%e7%a8%b1%e4%b8%8d%e5%b0%8b%e5%b8%b8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190529%2Fs00001%2F1559087939995%2F%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25aa%2592-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2588%25aa%25e9%25a3%259b%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%2594%25b0%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e6%25a9%259f3%25e5%25a4%25a96%25e9%259b%25b6%25e4%25bb%25b6%25e8%2584%25ab%25e8%2590%25bd-%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e7%2595%25b6%25e5%25b1%2580%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%25b0%258b%25e5%25b8%25b8&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=e731cc53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190529%2Fs00001%2F1559087939995%2F%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25aa%2592-%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2588%25aa%25e9%25a3%259b%25e6%2588%2590%25e7%2594%25b0%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e6%25a9%259f